</p>
<p>I like that! When you're testing your API, you're really eating your own
dog food. And that's a perfect time to think about the user-experience of
getting work done with it.</p>
<p>Try it one last time:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">php testing.php</div></code></pre>
<p>That looks great!</p>

    
